title: RESOLUTIONS CALLING ON THE PRESIDENT OF THE UNITED STATES TO RELEASE CONTINGENCY FUNDS FOR THE SUPPLEMENTAL NUTRITION ASSISTANCE PROGRAM FOR THE DURATION OF THE ONGOING FEDERAL GOVERNMENT SHUTDOWN

abstracts.abstract: Senate, October 30, 2025 -- Resolutions adopted by the Senate calling on the President of the United States to release contingency funds for the supplemental nutrition assistance program for the duration of the ongoing federal government shutdown (being the text of Senate, No. 2686, printed as amended)
